    <item>
      <title>越南共产党总书记的去世为他的下属提供了晋升最高职位的途径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/vietnam-party-chief-s-death-gives-his-enforcer-a-path-to-top-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南共产党总书记阮富仲的去世为这位前反腐官员提供了机会，让他接任这个一党制国家最重要的职位，而此时越南正寻求从中美竞争中获取最大利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/vietnam-party-chief-s-death-gives-his-enforcer-a-path-to-top-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 03:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索罗斯支持哈里斯，因为其他华尔街民主党人希望进行竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/rich-democrat-donors-question-rush-to-back-harris-after-biden-drops-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在乔·拜登决定退出总统竞选的几个小时内，从希拉里·克林顿到加文·纽瑟姆再到巨额捐助者乔治·索罗斯等许多民主党政坛大腕都纷纷加入拜登的行列，支持副总统卡马拉·哈里斯成为第一候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/rich-democrat-donors-question-rush-to-back-harris-after-biden-drops-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:05:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以下是拜登从辩论失败到退出的关键时刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/full-timeline-of-biden-dropping-out-key-moments-from-debate-to-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是美国历史上最糟糕的政治算计之一，总统乔·拜登打赌与唐纳德·特朗普的早期辩论将增加他的当选几率。结果适得其反，人们对他的年龄和敏锐度产生了担忧，并立即使他的最后竞选陷入危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/full-timeline-of-biden-dropping-out-key-moments-from-debate-to-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:46:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登退出后，曼钦考虑以民主党人身份竞选总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/manchin-weighs-presidential-run-as-democrat-after-biden-exits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位顾问透露，在总统乔·拜登宣布退出竞选后，西弗吉尼亚州参议员乔·曼钦正考虑重新加入民主党，争夺总统候选人提名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/manchin-weighs-presidential-run-as-democrat-after-biden-exits</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:40:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乔·拜登向希望他下台的民主党人屈服，颠覆美国政坛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-22/biden-drops-out-plunging-2024-us-election-into-uncharted-territory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[将接力棒交给卡马拉·哈里斯是一笔 9600 万美元的赌注，赌她能在历史上最短的总统竞选中为竞选注入活力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-22/biden-drops-out-plunging-2024-us-election-into-uncharted-territory</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:40:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯将在全国演讲中讨论南海、税收问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/marcos-to-address-south-china-sea-taxes-in-speech-to-nation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一将在国会发表第三次国情咨文，预计他推动经济发展和维护南海主权的计划将成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/marcos-to-address-south-china-sea-taxes-in-speech-to-nation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:15:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言加速推进新型保障性住房模式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/china-s-ruling-party-vows-to-accelerate-affordable-housing-model</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了创纪录的房地产低迷之后，中国执政党共产党承诺加快推行以租赁为主、增加经济适用房的新住房模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/china-s-ruling-party-vows-to-accelerate-affordable-housing-model</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:09:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯的首要任务：让民主党人团结起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/harris-first-task-get-emboldened-democrats-to-fall-in-line</link>
      <description><![CDATA[时间紧迫，党内紧张局势加剧，许多国会民主党人周日纷纷支持副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 作为他们选择的候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/harris-first-task-get-emboldened-democrats-to-fall-in-line</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 23:42:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总统退出竞选后，世界各国领导人赞扬拜登的政绩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/world-leaders-praise-biden-s-record-after-president-steps-aside</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登宣布自己 11 月不会竞选连任后，世界各国领导人纷纷向他致敬。他是自 1968 年以来第一位退出总统竞选的现任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/world-leaders-praise-biden-s-record-after-president-steps-aside</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 21:40:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特勤局局长因特朗普攻击事件接受议员质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/secret-service-chief-faces-lawmaker-grilling-over-trump-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国特勤局这位陷入困境的领导人即将面临来自敌对议员的猛烈质问，这些议员在前总统唐纳德·特朗普遭遇暗杀未遂后想让她辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/secret-service-chief-faces-lawmaker-grilling-over-trump-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 17:36:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
